191
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,399
Mother.

192
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,600
Don't be so superstitious.

193
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,840
As long as mother and child are safe...

194
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,799
