198
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,399
Yin Midwife.

199
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,799
Is there something wrong?

200
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:30,039
The child was born at the wrong time.

201
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:31,639
What do you mean, wrong?

202
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,840
When the child cried...

203
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:35,080
...it was exactly the midnight hour.

204
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,519
Before the midnight hour is Yang.

205
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,159
After it is Yin.

206
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,600
This child...

207
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:42,240
...was born right on the line between Yin and Yang.

208
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:45,480
Born in a Yin year, Yin month, Yin day, and Yin hour.

209
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,879
He has the Fate of Fourfold Yin Earth.

210
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,399
This...

211
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:50,960
...what does that mean?

212
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:51,759
This earth...

213
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,120
...is no ordinary earth.

214
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:56,759
